      "message": "Patch Set 3: Verified+1\n\nPassed enforced test review-ldiskfs-dne on CentOS 7.0/x86_64 uploaded by Onyx Autotest from onyx-36vm1: https://testing.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/15a51ecb-18ef-4e66-ab4e-36630a863085 ran 4 tests.",
